variables.name: RESULT_SUCCESS
variables.comment: * Indicates that the operation was successful.

variables.name: RESULT_ERROR_UNKNOWN
variables.comment:
* Indicates that setting or retrieving the call forwarding info failed with an unknown
         * error.

variables.name: RESULT_ERROR_FDN_CHECK_FAILURE
variables.comment:
* Indicates that call forwarding is not enabled because the recipient is not on a
         * Fixed Dialing Number (FDN) list.

variables.name: RESULT_ERROR_NOT_SUPPORTED
variables.comment: * Indicates that call forwarding is not supported on the network at this time.

methods.name: void onCallForwardingInfoAvailable(@NonNull CallForwardingInfo info)
methods.comment:
* Called when the call forwarding info is successfully retrieved from the network.
         * @param info information about how calls are forwarded

methods.name: void onError(@CallForwardingError int error)
methods.comment:
* Called when there was an error retrieving the call forwarding information.
         * @param error
